from ufoLib.glifLib to fontTools.ufoLib.glifLib. This keeps the code logic identical.

The LLM on the other hand Replaced ufoLib.glifLib.GlyphSet with fontTools.ttLib.TTFont.

GlyphSet is designed to read a directory of XML-based source files (UFO format). 
TTFont is designed to read a single binary file (TTF/OTF). 
Pointing TTFont at a directory will cause a FileNotFoundError or IsADirectoryError.

